reviewText: Love these movies. I read the books years ago and watched the movies on Lifetime. When I saw them on Amazon, I knew that I had to own them.
Have only watched Blue smoke but enjoyed it as much as the book.  Want to read the other books first and then will watch the other movies
I enjoyed all four movies very much. They are well done . I'm a big Nora Roberts fan.
I really like the collection and I wish they were more NOra Robert movies.
I love the nira roberts movies.
Not as good as the books, but still entertaining.
If you like Nora Roberts, you'll like this set!
I don't have any thing negative to say about my purchase.  The movies are in great shape.  I will most definitely be purchasing more!  Thank you
My mom is a fanatic of Nora Roberts and when she seen it on Lifetime and started talking about how she like those particular movies I just went to Amazon to see if it was available.
Great collection, perfect for weekend movie watching.
